Misc.

Early v. Tinsley, Warden. The Chief Justice is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Petitioner pro se. Duke W. Dunbar, Attorney General of Colorado, Frank E. Hickey, Deputy Attorney General, and J. F. Brauer, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.
